title: 32: No Such Thing As A Good Gift For Gordon Brown
content: Dan (@schreiberland), James (@jamesharkin), Andy (@andrewhunterm), Anna (@nosuchthing) and the composer of our theme tune, musician Ash Gardner (@emperor_yes) discuss useless Presidential gifts, great big arrows, Tom and Jerry’s sweet ending, and a passport carrying pharaoh.
